---
import SectionHeading from '../../../components/SectionHeading.astro';
---
<section class="bg-slate-900 py-16 text-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-10 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <SectionHeading
      eyebrow="Roadmap"
      title="Live rooms and tournaments on deck"
      description="Version 2 introduces real-time multiplayer rooms and seasonal tournaments. Infrastructure builds on Astro SSR routes, Astro DB, and optional WebSockets."
      align="center"
      titleClass="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl text-white"
      descriptionClass="mt-4 text-base text-white/70"
    />
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/10 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Live Rooms</h3>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-white/80">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-podcast text-amber-300"></i>
            <span>Host console controls pacing, question queues, and reveal animations.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-wifi text-amber-300"></i>
            <span>WebSocket broadcast keeps timers, scores, and reactions in sync.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-comments text-amber-300"></i>
            <span>Optional emoji reactions with moderation filters and slow mode.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/10 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Tournaments</h3>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-white/80">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-sitemap text-amber-300"></i>
            <span>Auto-generate brackets with group-stage seeding and elimination rounds.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-star text-amber-300"></i>
            <span>Custom scoring profiles weight accuracy, speed, and streaks differently.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-file-certificate text-amber-300"></i>
            <span>Export sponsor-ready leaderboards with theming, logo overlays, and share links.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
